==English==
===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} suffix [[-κίνησις]], from [[Ancient Greek]] [[κίνησις]] (''kinesis'') "motion, movememt", from [[κινέω]] (''kineo'') "to move, to put in motion".

===Suffix===
